{"type": "article", "id": 63964, "title": "小众内衣品牌威胁维密在美地位，以及，什么是 Club-leisure？| 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-05-22T11:01:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 20605, "name": "维密"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 43990, "name": "Adidas"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190522190012whcByfz35YRu0gZJ.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Prada-to-rationalise-wholesale-as-it-focuses-on-digital-seeks-price-uniformity,1101393.html#.XOUlMFMzb_Q\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 计划削减批发商渠道，强调数字化及统一售价</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Prada 在香港证交所发布的声明中表示，该公司计划在意大利本土乃至整个欧洲市场重新评估其批发商渠道。声明中并未提及具体细节，只说“集团认为在零售及数字渠道上确保定价政策的连贯性是至关重要的，最终目的是支持品牌持续且长期的增长”。路透社报道称，这意味着 Prada 计划减少批发商合作伙伴的数量，而手袋以及配饰业务将是受影响最大的部分。</p><p>过去 20 年，奢侈品行业一直在不断收紧品牌对于产品、形象乃至品牌价值的直接控制。对于 Prada 来说，这不仅意味着从一些多品牌集合店中撤出，也意味着留出的空白将被线上及电商合作伙伴取代。去年 3 月，Prada 还在直营店内停止进行季末折扣活动，以保护品牌的高端形象。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/stefan-larsson-pvh-president-tommy-hilfiger-calvin-klein-chirico-1203136320/\" rel=\"nofollow\">原 Ralph Lauren CEO 被任命为 PVH 集团总裁</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 从 6 月 3 日起，原 Ralph Lauren CEO Stefan Larsson 将担任 PVH 集团总裁，管理该集团旗下的 Tommy Hilfiger、Calvin Klein 等品牌，合约期为五年，向董事长兼 CEO Emanuel Chirico 汇报。后者计划在未来三到四年内将 CEO 职位交给 Stefan Larsson，本人仅担任董事长。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/victorias-secret-market-share-sinks-as-online-brands-grow-2019-05-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">维密在美市场份额下滑</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 根据 Coresight Research 的统计，维密去年在美国的市场份额已从 2013 年的 31.7% 降至 24%，受到 Aerie、ThirdLove、Adore Me 及 True &amp; Co. 等新兴小众品牌的挑战。这些小众品牌的份额已从 2013 年的 28.1% 增长至 36.2%，而 Nike、adidas 以及 Lululemon 则不断占领运动内衣市场，所占份额为 0.2%。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/sneaker/423993/zuikuaibenyueshangjiaoff-white-x-nike-waffle-racer-guanfangyulantushichu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Off-White x Nike Waffle Racer 发布官方预览图，最快将于本月发售。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221814207ho9kACZeYFVHRTX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181435moVEfBWFgeTsnjbd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181432yv7HdAczTSDXbPkm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181432cn0JROxbgjXqMrH9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/44564/1/adidas-originals-alexander-wang-season-five-collection-80s-clubbing-streetwear\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang&nbsp;与&nbsp;adidas Originals&nbsp;的联名系列进行到第五季。</a></strong><br></p><p>本季灵感来自 80 年代运动潮流。Alexander Wang <a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/44564/1/adidas-originals-alexander-wang-season-five-collection-80s-clubbing-streetwear\" rel=\"nofollow\">在接受 <em>Dazed</em> 采访时</a>将其形容为“Club-leisure”——适合在健身房、夜店以及这两个场景之间的任何场合穿着的服饰。这包括超大尺寸的帽衫、复古风运动裤和瑜伽裤、裹身裙以及一系列新廓形的球鞋。系列大片由&nbsp;Jonny Dufort&nbsp;摄影，Haley Wollens 造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180936JBtZV0HCNQ3uMK8G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180936k9EGoH2VZvzLTYjO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221809365AgJOVHEPw408R7k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180936PwJ3QdT1eHj0u7Sz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180937fOgC3Bp8rsK74W9D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180945yF4UGgv19WoX3l62.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522180945js3ixIRkyLBXmVTa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.494531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/424018/fugujiarifengkith-x-tommy-hilfiger-2019-chunxialianmingxilie-lookbook-fabu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH x Tommy Hilfiger 2019 春夏联名系列 Lookbook 发布。</a></strong></p><p>该系列将于美国东部时间 5 月 24 日 11 点于 KITH 门店和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://kith.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a>开售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522182322fUIL4Bmh7vluxOn3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522182323XTAr12PMEqDVYHfJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522182325devj91fP6NF2WihM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221823477jv9wRY364OtJMIX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221823275al2wHOUkoJ9Me8z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522182327I4OwtbWNcxs5dP3g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221823288nr5btBuVSwXPAvM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221823548bgY2VFDQc0E5aTN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522182406uO0PypxbAk6VrJXj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>5 月 19 日至 9 月 1 日期间，位于美国达拉斯的 <strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/423533/shizhuangmiburongcuoguodior-zuixinzhanlandenglu-dallas-museum-of-art/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dallas Museum of Art 将举办 Dior 主题展览《Dior: From Paris to the World》</a></strong>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181940GKREWH7VLMzIhimx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181939WOJ6dC7zceo8mNE0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181940L6sl7bjVXq9SRtK2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181951poDWM4f2gBebiqlH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019052218195196KfmIbYpaGvZlCU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522181951Rha6NCwJ4qlgeksZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://metalmagazine.eu/en/post/editorial/los-angeles-del-gimnasio-flavia-daniele\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Metal Magazine</em> 造型特辑：Los ángeles del gimnasio。</a></strong></p><p><strong>摄影：</strong>Flavia Daniele，造型：Jacopo Assaiante、Arianna Maver 以及 Sianna Georguieva。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175406xnkc6TZ2Ddho4C58.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175406YCQHizlu1e4qIK9Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221754173rRmOQGVLyjUg9Xk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221754287xWzaIjLKqTcVyhJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.638750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175417lYgtP4ULQRmsCiyM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175437yjMYth40W95xRPVE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.643750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175437jhBeRK38AVWxClLr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.630000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175438Xq1OVvMUmeAjwLRW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.644375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221755130xBu8EXe3c7zVOjv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.582591\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175524xvRmtkJPf7oWyG8s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.582591\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905221755302U1sF3bf8KkXVH5E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.254902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175529LI2ev56T7XVgmzEH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250977\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175530ZmoBuxF3k7gp0IHz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.573255\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175530tcQxPKAHlurNybjM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.256874\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190522175530psUBXWFH0Sk3tx41.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.272872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自 <em><a href=\"https://metalmagazine.eu/en/post/editorial/los-angeles-del-gimnasio-flavia-daniele\" rel=\"nofollow\">Metal Magazine</a></em><br></p>"}